# Random Facts Application

This application generates random facts on various topics.

## Getting Started

To run this application, you need to have Java 17 and Maven installed on your machine. Once you have installed these dependencies, follow the steps below:

1. Clone the repository to your local machine.
2. Navigate to the root directory of the application.
3. Run `mvn spring-boot:run` command to start the application.
4. Open your web browser and go to `http://localhost:8080`
5. Add /api/facts to get a single fact `http://localhost:8080/api/facts`
6. Add /api/facts{number} to get up to 10 facts for example -> `http://localhost:8080/api/facts/7`

## Technologies Used

- Java 17
- Spring Boot
- Maven
